\lambda^3 - 2\lambda - 1  = (\lambda-1)\left(\lambda-\frac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}\right)\left(\lambda-\frac{1-\sqrt{5}}{2}\right)
\alpha, \beta, \gamma
u_0 = 3, u_1 = 0, u_2 = 4
\alpha = \beta = \gamma = 1
u_n = \alpha (-1)^n + \beta \left(\frac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}\right)^n + \gamma \left(\frac{1-\sqrt{5}}{2}\right)^n
2 \mid u_2
